---
title: Put your Feet Up Chicken Breast Korma Traybake with Spiced Potatoes and Mango Slaw
description: Our Put your Feet Up Chicken Breast Korma Traybake only takes 10 minutes to prep. Once the veg is in the oven, make your slaw before baking the chicken for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
